Check all current PieHelper TTY configurations and attempt a repair where needed:confpieh_ph.sh -r | more
List all OS-relevant PieHelper modules and their current debugstate:confpieh_ph.sh -p list -m all | more
Switch the debug state for one or more relevant PieHelper modules:confpieh_ph.sh -p debug -m prompt
Discover supported applications and integrate them into PieHelper:confapps_ph.sh -p state
Go to Main menu:ph_show_menu Main
Go to Apps menu:ph_show_menu Apps
Go to OS menu:ph_show_menu OS
Go to Controllers menu:ph_show_menu Controllers
Return to previous screen:return
